am\": \"those Games\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The British women's rowing crew gradually closed the gap on the Netherlands after a fast start from the Dutch.\", \"from\": 496, \"to\": 606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 500, \"end\": 507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9979099007581204, \"rank\": 0.0018285274793004708, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 560, \"end\": 571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.8843916189601431, \"rank\": 0.13069889555711175, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 600, \"end\": 605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9907161506347365, \"rank\": 0.007974013965189956, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gap\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 552}, {\"ngram\": \"a fast start\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was anyone's race with 500 metres to go with the two crews neck and neck, and Britain looked as if they would just get the upper hand as they pushed for glory.\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 691, \"end\": 698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9930191691022927, \"rank\": 0.00702986848642679, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone's race\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 630}, {\"ngram\": \"500 metres\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngra